      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury sedan, offering a perfect balance of performance and executive comfort. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic that retains a deep, mirror-like gloss. While there are a few minor rock chips on the front hood consistent with standard highway use, the body panels are straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the Canberra Beige Dakota leather interior has been meticulously maintained; the seats remain firm with minimal bolster wear, and the cabin is strictly non-smoker with no pet odors. All technological features, including the high-resolution navigation, Harman Kardon surround sound, and gesture control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health with a documented service history. The turbocharged inline-six engine pulls cleanly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. It sits on 19-inch V-spoke wheels wrapped in Continental tires with plenty of tread depth remaining. This car has been garage-kept and recently underwent a full professional detail. Included are two key fobs, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a folder of maintenance receipts.",
